==English==
===Etymology===
From [[medieval]] {{L.}} ''[[ambrum]]'' "amber" or ''[[ambra grisea]]'' "grey amber".
===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-ambergris.ogg|Audio (US)}}
